<title>FACANG PHAL PUT IN CH212</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Zingka caan ah phun tuah, Dawtnak thlaici kha vorh, Chun caan an phun
 bangin, Zan caan zongah phun, Khawmhnak caan zong awt tuah, Hlehnak caan
 zong hngak tuah, Facang phal kha put in lawm in kan ra lai.

[C1]
   Facang phal put in, Facang phal put in, Facang phal kha put in lawm
   in kan ra lai, Facang phal put in, Facang phal put in, Facang phal kha
   put in lawm in kan ra lai.

[V2]
 Ni ceunak ah phun tuah, Thladem zongah phun tuah, Khuasik caan le
 minmei phan awk an si lo, Khawmh caan a phak tik-ah, Rian zong a dih cang
 lai, Facang phal kha put in lawm in kan ra lai.

[C2]
   Facang phal put in, Facang phal put in, Facang phal kha put in lawm
   in kan ra lai, Facang phal put in, Facang phal put in, Facang phal kha
   put in lawm in kan ra lai.

[V3]
 Tah pah in va kal tuah, Bawipa ca-ah phun tuah, Rawhnak nih kannih kan
 ngaihchiatter hmanhseh, Tahnak a dih tik-ah, Jesuh a kan lawmh lai,
 Facang phal kha put in lawm in kan ra lai.

[C3]
   Facang phal put in, Facang phal put in, Facang phal kha put in lawm
   in kan ra lai, Facang phal put in, Facang phal put in, Facang phal kha
   put in lawm in kan ra lai.</lyrics>
<key>C</key>
</song>